{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777079356561,"sessionID":"ses_23dd13d4effeAbA9Qd5a4CjcCr","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_2ikmzpeoxtLRLFqgx0a1bloT","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"category":"quick","command":"analyze-mode","description":"Explore workspace context","load_skills":[],"prompt":"Inspect D:\\agent_workspace to identify likely current active-work tracking mechanisms and workflow packages. Focus on project-manager, agent-workflow, agent-cli, or session/schedule related docs/configs. Summarize relevant files and how to tell whether there is active work or waiting/delegated work needing a schedule.","run_in_background":true,"session_id":"","subagent_type":""},"output":"Background task launched.\n\nBackground Task ID: bg_3f7f37f2\nDescription: Explore workspace context\nAgent: Sisyphus-Junior (category: quick)\nStatus: pending\n\nSystem notifies on completion. Use `background_output` with task_id=\"bg_3f7f37f2\" to check.\n\nDo NOT call background_output now. Wait for <system-reminder> notification first.\n\n<task_metadata>\nsession_id: ses_23dd0f3dbffeLhDXHOJrpdiqSD\ntask_id: bg_3f7f37f2\nbackground_task_id: bg_3f7f37f2\n</task_metadata>\n\nto continue: task(session_id=\"ses_23dd0f3dbffeLhDXHOJrpdiqSD\", load_skills=[], run_in_background=false, prompt=\"...\")","metadata":{"truncated":false,"prompt":"Inspect D:\\agent_workspace to identify likely current active-work tracking mechanisms and workflow packages. Focus on project-manager, agent-workflow, agent-cli, or session/schedule related docs/configs. Summarize relevant files and how to tell whether there is active work or waiting/delegated work needing a schedule.","agent":"Sisyphus-Junior","category":"quick","load_skills":[],"description":"Explore workspace context","run_in_background":true,"command":"analyze-mode","sessionId":"ses_23dd0f3dbffeLhDXHOJrpdiqSD","model":{"providerID":"MoreCode","modelID":"gemini-3-flash"}},"title":"Explore workspace context","time":{"start":177707935